               <msContents>
                  <summary>I) Introduction (fols. 2ra-3vb; 4r-5v)
 - Letter of Eusebius to
                     Carpianus (fol. 2ra-vb)
 - “Synopsis of Classes” (fols. 2vb-3vb)
 -
                     Canon tables (fols. 4r-5v)
 II) Gospel of Matthew (fols. 3v; 6r-44rc)
                     - List of the “tituli” for the Gospel of Matthew: 68 titles (fols. 3v,
                     6r-v)
 - Bǝsrāta Mātewos “Gospel of Matthew” (fols. 7ra-44rc)
 III)
                     Gospel of Mark (fols. 44v-72ra)
 - List of the “tituli” for the Gospel of
                     Mark: 48 titles (fols. 44v-45r)
 - Bǝsrāta Mārqos “Gospel of Mark” (fols.
                     46ra-72ra)
 IV) Gospel of Luke (fols. 72v-115rc)
 - List of the
                     “tituli” for the Gospel of Luke: 93 titles (fols. 72v-74r)
 - Bǝsrāta Luqās
                     (fols. 75ra-115rb)
 - Short postscript (fol. 115rc)
 V) Gospel of John
                     (fols. 115v-145rc)
 - List of the “tituli” for the Gospel of John: 18
                     titles (fol. 115v)
 - Bǝsrāta Yoḥannǝs “Gospel of John” (fols.
                     116ra-145rc).</summary>
